nodes.text: Lakbulbup was a male Chiss individual who was the cousin of the rancher Lakphro. Lakbulbup lived on the planet Naporar with his wife Dilpram, a scientist. Lakbulbup worked at the Expansionary Defense Fleet headquarters on Naporar.

Lakbulbup's job involved staying informed about military events. Lakphro sent Lakbulbup and his wife a nyix brooch from Haplif of the Agbui for metallurgical analysis. Upon receiving the brooch, Lakbulbup recommended they send the brooch to Senior Captain Mitth'raw'nuruodo for analysis of the artwork.
